--   <li>Maximum value length - 256 Unicode characters in UTF-8.</li>
--   <li>If your tagging schema is used across multiple services and

--   <li>Do not use <tt>aws:</tt>, <tt>AWS:</tt>, or any upper or lowercase

--   have this prefix. If a tag value has <tt>aws</tt> as its prefix but
--   the key does not, then Forecast considers it to be a user tag and will
--   count against the limit of 50 tags. Tags with only the key prefix of
